39:
The final World Flipper! It's... actually
here! I can't believe it.
43:
Wait a second—where the hell did
Adjudicus go? I don't see him!
48:
Adjudicus is no doubt off planning
something with the Lance... This is
our chance to restore Light's powers!
53: Please, Stella. We're counting on you!
70:
We... we did it! Light can turn back
into the Champion now!
77:
I... I'm sorry...
It's... no use...
84:
I see... It seems that a part of you is...
missing. Carved out, just like this
chasm.
87:
In your current state, you are a
broken vessel, likely incapable of
holding the power of the Champion.
92:
Every time we obtained a piece of
the starchart, I felt it. Deep down, I
knew something was wrong, but I
chose to banish the thought from
my mind.
94:
The light inside my body... is fading...
Leaking out...
98:
I can no longer call myself the
Champion, Alk! Don't you see? I'm
useless. Worthless!
108:
Grant me your power once again,
Stella. It is time for me to become
the bearer of the curse.
113:
Just what exactly are you trying to
do, Adjudicus?!
116:
The power of the curse is what
creates daemons... And its source
lies here, within the souls of our
fallen comrades.
119:
This is the only reason we fiends
have been able to survive so long.
We sustain ourselves on the energy
of the dead!
121:
Cruel though it may be, such is the
fate of those who live in this world.
To dream, to hope, only to be
purged.
143:
You bear the Antipode Lance? What
is the meaning of this, Adjudicus?
148:
How irritating. Come to me, Lance!
Heed my call!
153: What the... Stella?! Do not interfere!
157:
The spirits of the dead are destined
to one day fade away. The vestiges
you see in this world are merely lost
souls lingering in vain.
159:
But you chose to create a chasm
between the realms of the living and
the dead... This very abyss.
161:
The countless souls of purged fiends
that remain here... For ages they've
acted as the source of your power!
166:
So, you seek to usurp the power of
the curse?
167:
Do you truly think yourself up to the
task, Adjudicus?
171:
Do not forget that I once revered
you, uncle. The brand in my eye that
bears the power of the curse is proof
of my commitment.
174:
I shall take on the power of the
dead...
And become the new Lord of
Shadow!
186:
You... Why must you always get in
my way, Stella?! If it weren't for you...
190:
Get out of the way! Do you all have
a death wish or something?!
193:
So that's it, huh. If we help Adjudicus,
we get a brand new Lord of Shadow
in return?
198: Stella... Is this the right thing to do?
204:
I... I don't know. I just...
I don't want anyone else to die!
209:
I understand. Don't worry, Stella. We
will protect you!
